               <p>GEORGE STAPLETON. I live at <placeName id="t18320705-220-crimeloc1155">Brentford</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320705-220-crimeloc1155" type="placeName" value="Brentford"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320705-220-crimeloc1155" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320705-220-off1153 t18320705-220-crimeloc1155"></join>. On the 23rd of June, between ten and eleven o'clock, some persons came into my shop, and asked to look at a handkerchief, and then at some waistcoats; I missed a waistcoat before they left, and when they left, I looked out and saw the prisoner join them, within about fifty yards; I followed the prisoner, and took 
him with it.</p>


               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320705-220-person1835">
                  CHARLES 
                  WERNHAM
               <interp inst="t18320705-220-person1835" type="surname" value="WERNHAM"></interp>
