                  </persName>
             (Police-constable T 169). I received the prisoner in charge; I have the waistcoat, which has the prosecutor's mark on it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I bought it of a man who travels with articles.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320705-220-person1836">
                  GEORGE 
                  STAPLETON
               <interp inst="t18320705-220-person1836" type="surname" value="STAPLETON"></interp>
